title: Uncertainty
name: Uncertainty
description:
Students retreat to the Student Center to eat lunch and restrategize. The lockdown on the Main Building and the increased police presence has decreased the possibility of executing a sit-in successfully.  

There is a sense of urgency shot through with uncertainty. The sit-in participants know they must act today, while the board is meeting, or risk losing their momentum and support.

They decided to wait.
